text: Thæcring brrda phu thi klaw wa xallxh pen phu thi sam khxng sam xngkh nan di tkpen phu ptiseth sraththa læw mimi sing dı thi khwr di rab kar khearph sakkara nxkcak phu thi khwr khearph sakkara xngkh deiyw theanan læa hak phwk khea mi hyud yang cak sing thi phwk khea klaw nænxn brrda phu thi ptiseth kar sraththa nı hmu phwk khea nan ca txng prasb kar lngthosʹ xan cebsæb
